name: Modern Renaissance Palette
description: Anastasia Beverly Hills Modern Renaissance Eyeshadow Palette is an essential eyeshadow palette featuring 14 full-pigment shades ranging from neutral to berry-red eyeshadow hues in matte and metallic finishes. Inspired by the resins and paints of Renaissance art, this professional-quality eye makeup collection features an easy-to-blend formula in a versatile color range for creating endless eyeshadow looks, from subtle to dramatic pops of color. Included in the Modern Renaissance Eyeshadow Palette is a dual-ended brush and large mirror housed inside travel-friendly packaging.

name: Amrezy Palette
description: A limited-edition palette by Anastasia Beverly Hills’ that features 16 all-new shades so you can achieve everything from go-to daytime to ultra-glamorous looks.

name: Brow Wiz
description: An ultra-slim, retractable pencil for precise detailing and creating hair-like strokes.

name: Original Beautyblender
description: The original Beautyblender, this has become a beauty phenomenon – with its elliptical shape and super-strong sponge material allowing for flawless application of foundation, primer and BB/CC creams, it's a definite make up bag must-have. This gorgeous fuchsia incarnation will add an instant splash of colour to your cosmetic collection, applying and blending all kinds of make up products perfectly. Completely edgeless, it blends beautifully across large areas, as well as reach the smaller contours of your face. Just make sure you wet it first so that the material expands and won’t absorb your product – meaning it will end up on your face, not on the sponge. It's latex-free, non-irritating, non-allergenic, odourless, long-lasting and easily washable.

name: Champagne Bubbles Liquid Highlighter
description: This glowing liquid highlighter creates a luminous, soft focus finish that adds the perfect glow to your look. Infused with micro-fine diamond powder, the formula blends easily and seamlessly into the skin and wears well both under makeup or over foundation. Raise your glass to glowing skin all year long!

name: Pretty Fresh Hyaluronic Acid Tinted Moisturizer
description: ColourPop Pretty Fresh Tinted Moisturizer is a hydrating, oil-free tinted moisturizer with lightweight coverage that evens skintone and leaves your skin looking fresh and healthy. Formulated with hyaluronic acid (aka HA) and coconut water to support skin hydration without adding oil, this tinted moisturizer works for all skin types and makeup styles - just customize your routine to create your own look!

name: Pretty Fresh Creamy Concealer
description: this creamy, cushiony, full coverage concealer seamlessly blends into the skin leaving a natural, fresh finish. skin-loving, hyaluronic acid and coconut water hydrate the skin, while full coverage pigments cover and correct blemishes, this combo leaves you with fresh, perfected skin that lasts all day. oil free, dermatologist tested, and ideal for all skin types.

name: Face Essential Brush Set - Rose Gold
description: The Luxie Face Essentials Set was created to give you a complete, airbrushed face base. You'll buff, blend, contour, and set your way to an airbrushed, definied face.

name: Eye Essential Brush Set - Rose Gold
description: Create a variety of eye looks with this must-have set. From a classic smokey eye to the perfect winged eyeliner, this versatile kit will have you covered for all your favorite eye looks.

name: Baked Blush - Luminoso
description: Pigment packed powder blush which delivers a sheen of healthy luminosity. Applied to the apples of the cheeks, Baked Blush gives a sheer wash of soft colour for a naturally flushed complexion. Baked on Italian terracotta, the powder is incredibly finely milled for a silky application.

name: Baked Bronzer - Dolce
description: A finely milled face and body bronzer embellished with threads of gold shimmer. Created with its home heritage of Milan in mind the Baked Bronzer is created on Italian terracotta tiles to provide its unique silk-like texture. Streak-free and easily blendable, the formula ensures effortless application for an easy to achieve bronzed summer glow.

name: Make It Last Setting Spray
description: Lock in makeup's just-applied look for all day wear up to 16 hours with Milani Make It Last Setting Spray Prime + Correct + Set. Spray under makeup for a mattifying primer and over makeup for lasting, crease-free, fade-free wear in any climate.

name: Stellar Lights Highlighter Palette - Rose Glow
description: Be radiant with the Stellar Lights Highlighter Palette. Featuring a complementary trio of finely-milled, buildable powders, this palette offers multi-dimensional illuminating effects. Each richly-pigmented shade blends seamlessly over the skin and can be worn alone or together for customised looks.

name: Butter Gloss - Crème Brulée
description: This buttery soft, silky smooth & decadent fan favorite lip gloss delivers sheer to medium coverage that melts onto your lips. Never sticky and always supple and kissable, plus it stays put and won't feather! Gorgeous on its own, over your favorite lipstick or lip liner and comes in a bunch of gloss shades. Our Butter Gloss adds the perfect pop of shine to your makeup look.

name: Micro Brow Pencil
description: Build full beautiful brows with our ultra-thin Micro Brow Pencil. This micro mechanical brow pencil is so precise, it coats even the finest hairs with color for a natural-looking finish. Create more defined brows by filling in sparse, over tweezed areas. The super-skinny tip draws ultra fine lines, allowing you to create the look of natural brow hairs! In colors from taupe to blonde, black and beyond. Your arches will never look better after you fill them in with this creamy, high-pigmented micro brow pencil!

name: The Healthy Foundation SPF20
description: The Healthy Foundation SPF 20 by Physicians Formula is a long-wearing, buildable, and breathable foundation that provides lightweight, medium-to-full coverage with a healthy, satin finish.

name: Murumuru Butter Bronzer
description: Physicians Formula Murumuru Butter Bronzer is an ultra-luxurious bronzer infused with Murumuru Butter, delivering a radiant Brazilian goddess glow! Moisturizing wonder features ultra-refined pearl and soft-focus pigments that smooth skin texture, brighten skin tone and deliver a gorgeous bronze finish.

name: The Healthy Lip Velvet Finish - Bare With Me
description: Discover the Physicians Formula The Healthy Lip Velvet Liquid Lipstick, a decadent mousse-like texture lipstick delivers high-impact colour that glides on for seamless colour. The cream formula features avocado oil and hyaluronic acid.

name: Murmuru Butter Blush - Vintage Rouge
description: Discover the Physicians Formula Murumuru Butter Blush 7.5g a ultra-luxurious formula, infused with Murumuru Butter, delivers a radiant Brazilian goddess glow! Incredibly soft and ultra-creamy texture combines the best features of a powder and cream blush.

name: Shape Tape Concealer
description: Meet Tarte's iconic, Shape Tape Concealer & discover why one is sold every 12 seconds*! This vegan, full-coverage formula infused with tape technology instantly helps brighten, smooth & give the skin a firmer, more lifted look.

name: Amazonian Clay 12-Hour blush - Sensual
description: An award-winning powder blush that contains long-wearing Amazonian clay, so pigment looks freshly applied all day.

name: Peach Perfect Mattifying Setting Powder
description: This transfer-resistant, peach tinted-powder works to visibly brighten skin while creating a silky-smooth, matte finish that lasts up to 14 hours. For the first time in Too Faced history, they’ve created an entire line exclusively for Sephora. The Too Faced Peaches and Cream Comfort Matte Collection is infused with refreshing peaches and sweet fig milk—ingredients known for their hydrating and antioxidant-rich benefits—to help keep skin moisturized, comfortable, and beautifully matte.

name: Born This Way Foundation
description: An oil-free foundation that masterfully diffuses the line between makeup and skin with coverage so undetectable, they’ll think you were born this way.

name: Better Than Sex Mascara
description: An intensely black voluptuous volume mascara for the sexiest, defined, multidimensional lashes possible.

name: Better Than Sex Eyeliner
description: A cutting-edge liquid eyeliner that’s the easiest you’ll ever use, created to produce a sharp, fluid, smudge-proof line every time.

name: Hangover Primer
description: Hangover is a revolutionary makeup primer infused with coconut water, probiotic-based ingredients, and skin revivers that work together to boost skin’s radiance, promote elasticity, and help hydrate while locking down makeup for fresher, longer, and more flawless wear.

name: All Nighter Long-Lasting Makeup Setting Spray
description: With patented Temperature Control Technology, this weightless vegan mist lowers the temperature of your makeup—from foundation and concealer to eyeshadow and blush—to lock it in place. The result is smoother-looking skin and vibrant makeup that lasts all day or night.

name: All Nighter Primer
description: A smoothing and hydrating face primer that grips foundation into place and supports its staying power, so your look lasts all day.
